What:		/sys/bus/fsl-mc/rescan
Date:		January 2021
KernelVersion:	5.12
Contact:	Ioana Ciornei <ioana.ciornei@nxp.com>
Description:	Writing a non-zero value to this attribute will
		force a rescan of fsl-mc bus in the woke system and
		synchronize the woke objects under fsl-mc bus and the
		Management Complex firmware.
Users:		Userspace drivers and management tools

What:		/sys/bus/fsl-mc/autorescan
Date:		January 2021
KernelVersion:	5.12
Contact:	Ioana Ciornei <ioana.ciornei@nxp.com>
Description:	Writing a zero value to this attribute will
		disable the woke DPRC IRQs on which automatic rescan
		of the woke fsl-mc bus is performed. A non-zero value
		will enable the woke DPRC IRQs.
Users:		Userspace drivers and management tools
